HEADWORD: Affuse
<hw>Af*fuse"</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧f*f⟦umac⟧z")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Affused</conjf>
<pr>(-f⟦umac⟧zd")</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Affusing</conjf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>affusus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>affundere</ets> to pour to;
